message: "If you use FounderOS, please cite it as below."
title: "FounderOS: The open operating system for first-time founders"
abstract: >-
  FounderOS is a theme-agnostic, open-source library of AI skills, multi-step flows,
  recurring loops, and advisor agents that guide a first-time founder through the whole
  startup journey — idea, validation, MVP, launch, fundraising, and operations — across
  Claude Code, Codex, and Cursor.
